          "description": "This unit cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nThis unit cannot be poisoned.\n\nWhenever a Mori enters the battlefield from allied reinforcements, this unit will immediately have its TU reduced to 0, and be Purified (negative status effects like sleep, burn or poison are removed).\n\nWhen this unit enters battle, if there are at least 5 non-conjured units in the enemy team (including reinforcements), this unit adds 1 Kuromori to a random place in enemy reinforcements for each non-conjured enemy on the battlefield."
