        "found": true,
        "localization": {
          "name": "Dark and Light",
          "description": "If this unit would be defeated by an enemy attack or a status effect while having more than 1 HP, it instead survives with 1 HP.\n\nThis unit enters battle with Super Stealth. At the end of each of this unit's turns, this unit is granted Super Stealth.\n\nThis unit has 30% damage reduction, plus 10% for each ally Mori on the battlefield or in allied reinforcements (max of 70% while 4 Moris are on the battlefield or in allied reinforcements).\n\nIf this unit is below 25% of max HP at the end of a turn, and there is a Mori at the very end of allied reinforcements, that Mori will be sacrificed and all allies will be healed for 5% of max HP."
